# Types, enums, pattern matching, CRDTs, zones, temporal literals.

## A Point has:
    An x: Int.
    A y: Int.

## A Shape is one of:
    A Circle with radius Int.
    A Square with side Int.

## Main
Let p be a new Point with x 10 and y 20.
Set p's x to 5.
Show p's x.
Let s be a new Circle with radius 10.
Inspect s:
    When Circle (r):
        Show r.
    Otherwise:
        Show "other".
Let maybe be some 30.
Inspect maybe:
    When OptionSome (v):
        Show v.
    When OptionNone:
        Show none.
Let deadline be 2026-05-20 at 4pm.
Sleep 500ms.
Inside a zone called "Scratch":
    Let tmp be a copy of p.
Merge remote into local.
Increase c's points by 10.
Append "Line 1" to doc's lines.
